&lt;p&gt;The same failure occurred:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/5ce9b330-6874-11e3-a9a3-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/5ce9b330-6874-11e3-a9a3-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
